PAY television service provider, GOtv Nigeria, has announced a new discount offer, MAX Enjoyment for Less, for new customers starting from Thursday, March 3. According to a statement on Thursday from the firm, the decoder price, which was previously N9,500 has been discounted to N6,500, with a GOtenna and a one-month GOtv Max package as additional benefits to subscribers. The discount, which is available for a limited time, serves as a way to encourage new customers to get access to GOtv’s bouquet of quality entertainment. The statement quoted the Chief Executive Officer, MultiChoice Nigeria, John Ugbe, as saying that “We are aware of the current economic situation in the country and are constantly seeking avenues to make available quality entertainment at pocket friendly prices. “This discount creates a window for new customers to join the GOtv world of entertainment and remain connected to quality programming with family and friends.”